articles.title: US ski star Mikaela Shiffrin wins 2nd straight World Cup slalom of Olympic season
articles.description:
“I think it’s some of the best slalom skiing I ever did,” said Shiffrin, who got her 66th World Cup win in slalom and 103rd overall, both are records.

The post US ski star Mikaela Shiffrin wins 2nd straight World Cup slalom of Olympic season appeared first on Boston.com.
